						<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Assault weapon</span></h1>
						<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-navigation">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">This article is about the <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a> legal and political term.  For fully automatic military rifles, see <a href="/wiki/Assault_rifle" title="Assault rifle">Assault rifle</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Assault_weapon_(disambiguation)" title="Assault weapon (disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig">Assault weapon (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
