<li id="cite_note-AWA1988conc-30"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-AWA1988conc_30-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.vpc.org/studies/awaconc.htm">"Assault Weapons and Accessories in America"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Violence_Policy_Center" title="Violence Policy Center">Violence Policy Center</a>. 1988<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved February 26, 2005</span>. "Assault weapons—just like armor-piercing bullets, machine guns, and plastic firearms—are a new topic. The weapons' menacing looks, coupled with the public's confusion over fully automatic machine guns versus semi-automatic assault weapons—anything that looks like a machine gun is assumed to be a machine gun—can only increase the chance of public support for restrictions on these weapons. In addition, few people can envision a practical use for these weapons."</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAssault+weapon&amp;rft.btitle=Assault+Weapons+and+Accessories+in+America&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vpc.org%2Fstudies%2Fawaconc.htm&amp;rft.pub=Violence+Policy+Center&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Gunindustry_introduced-31"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Gunindustry_introduced_31-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation news">Richman, Josh (January 18, 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_22396050/assault-weapons-what-are-they-and-should-they">"Assault Weapons: What Are They, and Should They Be Banned?"</a>. <i>San Jose Mercury News</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved January 19, 2013</span>. "In fact, the term was introduced by the gun industry itself to boost interest in new lines of firearms."</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAssault+weapon&amp;rft.atitle=Assault+Weapons%3A+What+Are+They%2C+and+Should+They+Be+Banned%3F&amp;rft.aulast=Richman%2C+Josh&amp;rft.au=Richman%2C+Josh&amp;rft.date=January+18%2C+2013&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mercurynews.com%2Fnation-world%2Fci_22396050%2Fassault-weapons-what-are-they-and-should-they&amp;rft.jtitle=San+Jose+Mercury+News&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
